---
title: Charred Scallion and Corn Flatbread with Summer Squash and Salsa Fresca
description: As our chefs, Freida and Nate, were experimenting in the kitchen one afternoon, they thought, “What would happen if we took all the summer flavors we love and put them together on a flatbread? What would that taste like?” And voila! This smoky charred scallion, corn, and squash feast was born.
